{"type":"message","id":"390e5091","parentId":"48a9b345","timestamp":"2026-05-15T03:49:35.137Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sub-agent tried to run the bat file, but Unity refused because another instance (PID 20280) already has the same project open.\n\nI need to notify the group about this. The message should go to the group `oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77` in the dev group.\n\nThe sub-agent couldn't send the message directly (it didn't have the feishu messaging tool). I need to send the notification.\n\nLet me check if there's a feishu skill for sending messages... Looking at the available skills:\n- feishu-doc: Feishu document read/write\n- feishu-drive: Feishu cloud storage\n- feishu-perm: Feishu permission management\n- feishu-wiki: Feishu knowledge base\n\nNone of these are for sending chat messages. The channel is feishu, so sending a message back to the channel should happen naturally when I reply in the current session. But I need to send to a specific group.\n\nActually, looking at the runtime info: `channel=feishu`. So my replies in this session go back to the feishu channel. But the message from 小骑士 came from a specific group chat. When I reply, it should go back to that same group.\n\nWait, let me re-read the message. The message_id indicates it's from a specific message in feishu. If I reply in this session, it should go to the same channel (the group chat).\n\nLet me just provide a clear update in my reply. I'll explain that the update failed because Unity Editor is already open with the same project, and they need to close it first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"子 agent 跑完了，但 Unity 编辑器开着同一个项目，流水线没法跑。我来通知群里。\n\n小骑士，更新测试服失败了 ❌\n\n**原因：** Unity Editor 当前正在打开同一个项目（`E:/Solo/nightoffullmoon/client/cardv`），Unity 不允许重复打开同一项目。\n\n**需要：** 先关闭当前正在运行的 Unity Editor，再重新跟我说「更新测试服」就好。\n\n或者主人看到的话，需要我帮你关 Unity 可以直接说～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deep