{"type":"message","id":"fe517424","parentId":"8e2cd167","timestamp":"2026-05-15T07:18:56.526Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"小骑士又在群里说\"更新测试服\"了。根据流程（已更新）：\n\n1. 先回复\"收到\"\n2. 检查是否有热更流水线正在执行\n3. 关掉所有 Unity Editor 进程（kill Unity.exe 进程）\n4. git pull\n5. 运行 Unity 热更流水线（通过 sub-agent 执行 bat 文件）\n6. 完成后 @兵王 通知\n\n不过我注意到聊天历史里主人（Yousan）说\"测试服更新完成\" @小骑士，看起来主人可能已经手动更新过了？但小骑士还是要求更新，那就走流程吧。\n\n先回复\"收到\"，然后开始执行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，开始更新测试服流程～🌸"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_FcOkM7xD9vMPwIGNFZ949457","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"收到，开始更新测试服～🌸\nStep 1: 检查热更流水线 + 关闭 Unity Editor..."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":26004,"output":232,"cacheRead":3584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29820,"cost":{"input":0.00364056,"output":0.00006496,"cacheRead":0.000100352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0038058720000000005}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778829531705,"responseId":"ea97c3ee-5c67-4181-92e8-239af1df99d9"}}
