{"type":"message","id":"863cbfbd","parentId":"d85541b5","timestamp":"2026-05-15T07:45:43.704Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, now I have a clearer picture from the sub-agent's history. Let me piece together what happened:\n\nFrom the sub-agent's thinking it did:\n1. Fixed the Unity path in the bat file (changed `2020.3.49f1c1` to `2020.3.49f1`)\n2. Ran the bat file via Start-Process\n3. Bat started Unity (PID 17676) at 15:20:56\n4. Unity ran the pipeline - started with Lua merge, then moved to BuildAssetBundles\n5. The pipeline built asset bundles (SpriteAtlasPacking) \n6. The log file grew to 37,605,732 bytes (359,704 lines) at 15:34:26\n7. Unity exited (PID 17676)\n8. A second Unity process (PID 23816) appeared at 15:34:31 but was unrelated\n\nSo the sub-agent ran the bat but the bat had the wrong Unity path (`2020.3.49f1c1` instead of `2020.3.49f1`). The sub-agent fixed it.\n\nWait - but I looked at the bat file and it says:\n```\nset \"UNITY_PATH=C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Unity.exe\"\n```\nThis is the correct path. The sub-agent's thinking mentioned it changed from `2020.3.49f1c1` to `2020.3.49f1` - maybe the original bat had `2020.3.49f1c1`?\n\nActually, looking at my earlier read of the bat file, it says `2020.3.49f1`. So the sub-agent either read a different version or changed it.\n\nAnyway, the key finding is:\n- Unity started (PID 17676) at 15:20:56\n- It ran the pipeline, building asset bundles\n- The log stopped at 15:34:26 with SpriteAtlasPacking\n- Then Unity exited\n\nThe log ends without any completion message. Looking at the sub-agent's investigation, it was trying to figure out why Unity exited.\n\nNow, the sub-agent timed out (25 minutes). The result is \"timed out\" with partial progress.\n\nLet me look at what we know:\n1. The bat was run successfully\n2. Unity started and ran the pipeline (BuildAssetBundles phase at least)\n3. Unity exited at some point\n4. The CDN didn't get updated (D:\\cdn_solo hasn't been modified since March)\n\nBut wait - I already killed the sub-agent before it timed out. That's why it shows \"aborted\" in the last message and then \"timed out\".\n\nThe important thing is: where did the output go? The log file LastWriteTime was 15:34, but the sub-agent started at ~15:20 and the fix to the bat file path was applied... actually wait, the sub-agent tried to fix the bat file path and then ran the bat again?\n\nLet me look at this more carefully from the sub-agent history. It had 50 tool calls before timeout. Let me check if there was more output I missed.\n\nActually, I already killed the sub-agent with `subagents(action=kill)`. So the completion event coming now saying \"timed out\" is because I killed it.\n\nThe bottom line: the pipeline ran (partially). Unity exited but the CDN wasn't uploaded. Let me just tell the group the current status: the Unity batch process seems to have exited before completing the CDN upload step.\n\nActually wait - let me re-examine the situation. The sub-agent mentioned it fixed the Unity path. This is important because maybe the bat file actually has a wrong path and needs fixing. Let me check.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_tMNNfcpnKEI5xFPrchXn2698","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":29912,"output":870,"cacheRead":32768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63550,"cost":{"input":0.00418768,"output":0.0002436,"cacheRead":0.000917504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0053487840000000005}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778831132378,"responseId":"519ff3fa-d38b-44fb-8575-69818a6b8c17"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3e64ec08","parentId":"863cbfbd","timestamp":"2026-05-15T07:45:43.719Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_tMNNfcpnKEI5xFPrchXn2698","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@echo off\r\nchcp 65001 >nul 2>&1\r\nsetlocal\r\n\r\n:: 与 PlatformSwitcher.bat 一致：按本机安装修改 Unity 路径\r\nset \"UNITY_PATH=C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Unity.exe\"\r\n\r\ncd /d \"%~dp0\" || exit /b 1\r\nset \"PROJECT_PATH=%CD%\"\r\nset \"LOG_FILE=%PROJECT_PATH%\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\"\r\n\r\nif not exist \"%UNITY_PATH%\" (\r\n    echo [ERROR] 未找到 Unity.exe，请编辑本 bat 中的 UNITY_PATH。\r\n    exit /b 1\r\n)\r\n\r\necho [INFO] projectPath=%PROJECT_PATH%\r\necho [INFO] 执行无参 RunHotUpdatePipeline：流水线「热更」的全部有效步骤\r\necho [INFO] log=%LOG_FILE%\r\n\r\n\"%UNITY_PATH%\" -batchmode -quit -nographics -projectPath \"%PROJECT_PATH%\" -executeMethod YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline -logFile \"%LOG_FILE%\"\r\n\r\necho [INFO] Unity 退出码: %ERRORLEVEL%\r\nexit /b %ERRORLEVEL%\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778831143719}}
{"type":"message","id":"8740c03a","parentId":"3e64ec08","timestamp":"2026-05-15T07:45:49.207Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The bat file has `2020.3.49f1` not `2020.3.49f1c1`. But the sub-agent's thinking said it changed `2020.3.49f1c1` to `2020.3.49f1`. Looking at my USER.md, it says the project uses `Unity 2020.3.49f1c1`. Let me check the actual Unity installation path to see which one exists.\n\nActually, the bat checks `if not exist \"%UNITY_PATH%\"` - so if the path was wrong, it would have exited with an error before trying to run Unity. But the sub-agent managed to start Unity (PID 17676), so the path was correct after the fix.\n\nBut looking again - the bat file NOW has `2020.3.49f1` in it. So either the sub-agent fixed it (changed from `f1c1` to `f1`) and it's now saved, or it was always `f1`. But the sub-agent mentioned \"Changed 2020.3.49f1c1 to 2020.3.49f1\".\n\nLet me check the actual Unity installation to see what's there.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_OemzhedeXrQXww1SZD9B7672","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\\" -Directory | Select-Object Name; Test-Path \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Unity.exe\"; Test-Path \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1c1\\Editor\\Unity.exe\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":371,"output":399,"cacheRead":63488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64258,"cost":{"input":0.00005194,"output":0.00011172000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001777664,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001941324}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778831143723,"responseId":"29f62fb6-da1b-4031-a782-a05ffd714884"}}
