{"type":"message","id":"a0dbaba1","parentId":"2f7a6fe3","timestamp":"2026-05-15T07:46:14.797Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, no exit code found. Let me try to search the Editor.log for any relevant info more broadly. But first, let me look at when the Editor.log was last modified to see if it was from the batchmode run.\n\nActually wait - the Editor.log was last written at 15:40:55, which is AFTER the batchmode log stopped at 15:34:26. This means the Editor.log is from a different Unity instance (probably the one that was re-opened by someone, or maybe it's from the batchmode run and continued after).\n\nActually, what might have happened:\n1. Unity batchmode started at ~15:20 (PID 17676)\n2. Ran BuildAssetBundles \n3. Around 15:34, the pipeline wanted to run the CDN step which involves FTP/git operations\n4. Something went wrong (network issue? FTP credentials?)\n5. Unity exited\n\nBut we don't have the exit code. The bat should have captured it but since the sub-agent ran the bat in a sandboxed exec, we can't see its output directly.\n\nLet me just report the current status to the group. It seems the pipeline ran partially but didn't complete. The CDN wasn't updated. I should let the group know.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，目前的情况：\n\n✅ Unity Editor 已关闭，没有冲突\n✅ git pull 已更新到最新\n⚠️ Unity 热更流水线已经跑了（打资源阶段有输出），**但日志在 15:34 就停了，CDN 没有更新**（`D:\\cdn_solo` 还是三月的版本）\n\n而且 Unity 进程已经退出了，看起来是中途异常退出了，没有走完上传 CDN 的步骤。要不再试一次？或者主人手动跑一下看看具体报什么错？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":36,"output":379,"cacheRead":65408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65823,"cost":{"input":0.00000504,"output":0.00010612000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001831424,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019425839999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778831167946,"responseId":"76f09d55-ee57-40e3-a95b-8489b310d68e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f7d67274","parentId":"a0dbaba1","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:49:10.593Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f452ad0b8b0b48eaff93423b59]\nYousan(叶枝君): 开个bug单给<at user_id=\"ou_fc5144301797fb813a1fee33e1130ac3\">小骑士(谭佳钦)</at> , \"卡组私密无法选中\"\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_ce4d531e8b43b6ea580e3e12dedba0a6\", that mention refers to you.]\n\n[System: Your reply will automatically @mention: 小骑士(谭佳钦). Do not write @xxx yourself.]"}],"timestamp":1778849350591}}
