{"type":"message","id":"4cc426dd","parentId":"ef352133","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:49:16.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人让我在 TAPD 开个 bug 单给小骑士(谭佳钦)，标题是\"卡组私密无法选中\"。\n\n我需要使用 TAPD 自动提单的功能。从我之前的记忆中，TAPD 自动提单的进度是：\n- 已经安装 Playwright\n- 已经配置好扫码登录（微信扫码）\n- 但还没走通完整的提单流程\n\n让我检查一下 TAPD skill 和相关配置。\n\n从 MEMORY.md 的记忆：\n- Skill 路径：`~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/`\n- 工作区 ID：`31253609`（月圆之夜）\n- 创建缺陷 URL：`/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/add`\n- 模板 ID：`1131253609001000011`\n- 用户 ID：叶枝君=`1415287364`，周以天=`1166740146`\n- 表单字段：title/priority/version/module/branch/handler\n- 提交按钮：`#save_return`（\"提交&返回\"）\n- Cookies 路径：`workspace/tapd_cookies.json`\n\n不过之前说微信扫码登录还没走通完整的提单流程。让我先读取 TAPD skill 看看。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_xauE3DIrpWG7scDfSFa88726","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":59335,"output":328,"cacheRead":6912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66575,"cost":{"input":0.0083069,"output":0.00009184,"cacheRead":0.00019353599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008592276}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778849350594,"responseId":"9b83fdff-3789-48f1-829f-9decff841c79"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ba8cc86","parentId":"4cc426dd","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:49:16.703Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_xauE3DIrpWG7scDfSFa88726","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: tapd-bug-create\ndescription: Create bug tickets on TAPD (腾讯敏捷产品研发平台) for the 月圆之夜 project via Playwright browser automation. Use when user says: create a bug, file a bug, report a bug, 提单, 提bug, 创建缺陷. Also handles TAPD login and cookie management.\n---\n\n# TAPD Bug Create\n\nAutomate creating bug tickets on TAPD for workspace `31253609` (月圆之夜).\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n- **Cookies**: Valid TAPD login cookies in `workspace/tapd_cookies.json`\n- **Playwright**: Installed (v1.60.0+)\n- **WAF Bypass**: Requires anti-detection stealth script for headless mode; use `headless: false` for reliability\n\n## Workflow\n\n### Step 1: Check/Refresh Login\n\n```mjs\n// Check if cookies are valid\nconst page = await loadTapdPage('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/add');\n// If WAF blocked, use headed mode or re-login\n```\n\nIf login expired, use WeChat QR or SMS code login (see references/tapd-login.md).\n\n### Step 2: Create Bug\n\nRun the bundled script with bug parameters:\n\n```bash\nnode scripts/create_bug.mjs --title \"Bug title\" --priority \"P1\" --version \"【1V1】正式版本V2.0\" --module \"1V1\" --handler \"叶枝君\"\n```\n\nOr call the exported function:\n\n```mjs\nimport { createBug } from './scripts/create_bug.mjs';\nawait createBug({\n  title: 'Bug title',\n  priority: 'P1',\n  version: '【1V1】正式版本V2.0',\n  module: '1V1',\n  branch: 'master',\n  handler: '1415287364',     // 叶枝君's user ID\n  description: 'Bug details',\n});\n```\n\n### Step 3: Verify\n\nThe script returns the created bug URL. Confirm success by checking the bug list or the returned detail URL.\n\n## Key Configuration\n\n| Setting | Value |\n|---------|-------|\n| Workspace ID | `31253609` |\n| Template ID | `1131253609001000011` |\n| User ID (叶枝君) | `1415287364` |\n| User ID (周以天) | `1166740146` (兵王) |\n| Bug create URL | `/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/add` |\n| Cookies file | `workspace/tapd_cookies.json` |\n| Storage state | `workspace/tapd_storage.json` |\n\n## Bug Fields\n\nSee `references/bug-fields.md` for all available fields and their accepted values.\n\n## Anti-WAF Measures\n\nThe TAPD WAF (腾讯云WAF) blocks headless browser automation. Use:\n\n1. **Headless mode** (preferred for automation): Apply the stealth init script (see `create_bug.mjs` for the complete list of `addInitScript` properties)\n2. **Headed mode** (fallback): Set `headless: false` - always works\n\nIf WAF blocks headless mode, retry - it sometimes passes on subsequent attempts.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778849356703}}
{"type":"message","id":"461facc4","parentId":"3ba8cc86","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:49:18.299Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the available scripts and see what's needed. First, let me check the cookies file and the create_bug script.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_i5mWFI7OX3rtUcFmt91O6810","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/scripts/create_bug.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":737,"output":91,"cacheRead":66560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67388,"cost":{"input":0.00010318000000000001,"output":0.000025480000000000003,"cacheRead":0.00186368,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00199234}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778849356704,"responseId":"8a12eaca-d716-4726-aca4-63102e81b3b9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b4d37c91","parentId":"461facc4","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:49:18.307Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_i5mWFI7OX3rtUcFmt91O6810","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '../../..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\n\nconst STEALTH_INIT = () => {\n  delete navigator.webdriver;\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => false });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'languages', { get: () => ['zh-CN', 'zh'] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'hardwareConcurrency', { get: () => 8 });\n  window.chrome = { runtime: {}, loadTimes: function(){}, csi: function(){}, app: {} };\n};\n\n/**\n * Create a TAPD bug ticket\n * @param {Object} options\n * @param {string} options.title - Bug title (required)\n * @param {string} [options.priority] - P0/P1/P2/P3\n * @param {string} [options.version] - Version report, e.g. \"【1V1】正式版本V2.0\"\n * @param {string} [options.module] - Module, e.g. \"1V1\"\n * @param {string} [options.branch] - Branch, e.g. \"master\"\n * @param {string} [options.handler] - Handler user ID, e.g. \"1415287364\"\n * @param {string} [options.description] - Bug description\n * @param {string} [options.cc] - CC user ID\n * @param {boolean} [options.headless] - Use headless mode (default: false for reliability)\n * @returns {Promise<string>} Created bug detail URL\n */\nexport async function createBug(options) {\n  const { title, priority, version, module: mod, branch, handler, description, cc, headless = false } = options;\n  \n  if (!title) throw new Error('Bug title is required');\n  \n  // Load cookies\n  let cookies;\n  try {\n    cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  } catch (e) {\n    throw new Error(`Cookies not found at ${COOKIES_FILE}. Run login flow first.`);\n  }\n  \n  const browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']\n  });\n  \n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({\n    locale: 'zh-CN',\n    viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 },\n    userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/125.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n  });\n  \n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  await page.addInitScript(STEALTH_INIT);\n  \n  try {\n    // Load bug create page\n    const url = `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/bugtrace/bugs/add`;\n    await page.goto(url, { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 }).catch(() => {});\n    await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n    \n    const pageTitle = await page.title();\n    if (pageTitle.includes('WAF')) {\n      if (headless) {\n        console.log('WAF blocked in headless, retry with headless:false');\n        await browser.close();\n        return createBug({ ...options, headless: false });\n      }\n      throw new Error('WAF blocked - try again or use headed mode');\n    }\n    \n    // Fill fields\n    await page.fill('#BugTitle', title);\n    if (version) await page.selectOption('#BugVersionReport', version);\n    if (priority) await page.selectOption('#BugPriority', priority);\n    if (mod) await page.selectOption('#BugModule', mod);\n    if (branch) await page.selectOption('#BugCustomFieldOne', branch);\n    \n    if (handler) {\n      await page.evaluate((id) => {\n        const h = document.querySelector('#BugCurrentOwner');\n        if (h) { h.value = id; h.dispatchEvent(new Event('change', { bubbles: true })); }\n      }, handler);\n    }\n    \n    if (cc) {\n      await page.evaluate((id) => {\n        const c = document.querySelector('#BugCc');\n        if (c) { c.value = id; c.dispatchEvent(new Event('change', { bubbles: true })); }\n      }, cc);\n    }\n    \n    if (description) {\n      await page.evaluate((desc) => {\n        const d = document.querySelector('#BugDescription');\n        if (d) { d.value = desc; d.dispatchEvent(new Event('input', { bubbles: true })); }\n      }, description);\n    }\n    \n    // Submit\n    await page.evaluate(() => {\n      const btn = document.querySelector('#save_return');\n      if (btn) btn.click();\n    });\n    \n    await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n    const resultUrl = page.url();\n    \n    if (!resultUrl.includes('bugtrace/bugs/add')) {\n      return resultUrl;\n    } else {\n      const errors = await page.evaluate(() => {\n        return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.error,[class*=error]'))\n          .map(e => e.textContent?.trim()).filter(Boolean);\n      });\n      throw new Error(`Bug creation failed: ${errors.join(', ') || 'form validation error'}`);\n    }\n  } finally {\n    await browser.close();\n  }\n}\n\n// CLI support\nif (process.argv[1] === __filename) {\n  const args = {};\n  for (let i = 2; i < process.argv.length; i += 2) {\n    const key = process.argv[i].replace(/^--/, '');\n    args[key] = process.argv[i + 1];\n  }\n  \n  createBug(args).then(url => {\n    console.log('Bug created:', url);\n    process.exit(0);\n  }).catch(e => {\n    console.error('Failed:', e.message);\n    process.exit(1);\n  });\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778849358307}}
{"type":"message","id":"9ac6a398","parentId":"b4d37c91","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:49:20.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so the create_bug.mjs script:\n1. Loads cookies from `workspace/tapd_cookies.json` \n2. Opens TAPD page\n3. Fills in the form\n4. Submits\n\nThe cookies file needs to exist. Let me check if it does and if it's still valid.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_undzOovDvutxjuDzrjzU0906","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Test-Path \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tapd_cookies.json\"; Test-Path \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tapd_storage.json\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1504,"output":181,"cacheRead":67328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69013,"cost":{"input":0.00021056000000000002,"output":0.00005068,"cacheRead":0.001885184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002146424}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778849358308,"responseId":"69698657-e589-4b1e-8397-bbdab00d2cec"}}
