{"type":"message","id":"de272bc0","parentId":"7e74e225","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:49:24.418Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cookies and storage files exist. But the skill says cookies might have expired. Let me check the cookies expiry and see if they're still valid. Also, let me check the skill's login reference to see if I need to re-login.\n\nActually, the MEMORY.md says:\n\"⏳ **待完成：** 扫码登录后走通提单流程\"\n\nSo the login flow was done (微信扫码 was shown successfully) but the full bug creation flow hasn't been tested/verified end-to-end.\n\nLet me try to create the bug. I'll run the script with the appropriate parameters.\n\nFor the bug:\n- Title: \"卡组私密无法选中\"\n- Handler: 小骑士(谭佳钦) - I need to find their TAPD user ID\n- Other fields: I'll need reasonable defaults\n\nFirst, let me check the references/bug-fields.md for available values.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_RrCqgxuPUCZx961IRGKT2213","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/references/bug-fields.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":37,"output":251,"cacheRead":68992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69280,"cost":{"input":0.00000518,"output":0.00007028000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0019317759999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002007236}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778849360916,"responseId":"a31c555f-c5cb-43f3-ab2d-17d13118f6e2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f05253e","parentId":"de272bc0","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:49:24.428Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_RrCqgxuPUCZx961IRGKT2213","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TAPD Bug Fields (月圆之夜 Workspace 31253609)\n\n## Default Bug Template\n\nBased on bug #1016508 (【1v1】长手机上点击其他人信息显示错误):\n\n| Field | Default Value |\n|-------|---------------|\n| 发现版本 | `【1V1】正式版本V2.0` |\n| 处理人 | `叶枝君` (user_id: `1415287364`) |\n| 抄送人 | `周以天` (user_id: `1166740146`) |\n| 优先级 | `P2` |\n| 研发分支 | `YZY_1V1 V1.0 Beta` |\n| 模块 | `1V1` |\n| 描述 | (empty) |\n\n## Form Field Mapping\n\n| Field | HTML ID | Form Name | Type | Required |\n|-------|---------|-----------|------|----------|\n| 标题 | `#BugTitle` | `data[Bug][title]` | text | ✅ |\n| 发现版本 | `#BugVersionReport` | `data[Bug][version_report]` | select | ✅ |\n| 处理人 | `#BugCurrentOwner` (hidden) | `data[Bug][current_owner]` | hidden | ✅ |\n| 处理人(显示) | `#BugCurrentOwnerValue` | (none) | text | - |\n| 抄送人 | `#BugCc` (hidden) | `data[Bug][cc]` | hidden | |\n| 优先级 | `#BugPriority` | `data[Bug][priority]` | select | ✅ |\n| 研发分支 | `#BugCustomFieldOne` | `data[Bug][custom_field_one]` | select | ✅ |\n| 模块 | `#BugModule` | `data[Bug][module]` | select | ✅ |\n| 描述 | `#BugDescription` (hidden textarea) | `data[Bug][description]` | hidden | |\n| 关联需求 | `#BugStoryRelationBugStoryRelationRelativeId` | `data[BugStoryRelation][BugStoryRelation_relative_id]` | hidden | |\n| template_id | (hidden) | `data[template_id]` | hidden | ✅ |\n\n## Priority Values\n\n| Label | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| P0 | `P0` |\n| P1 | `P1` |\n| P2 | `P2` |\n| P3 | `P3` |\n\n## Version Report Options\n\nCommon values:\n- `【1V1】正式版本V2.0`\n- `【S11.6】商业化版本`\n- `【V2.0线上热更】`\n- `【0528周版本】`\n- `【1V1】正式版本V3.0`\n- `【0618周版本】`\n- `【0611周版本】`\n- `【0604周版本】`\n- `【0521周版本】`\n- `【S12.0】`\n- `【单机】A1.2`\n- `【需求池】`\n- `【B0.5】`\n\n## Module Options\n\n- `运营`\n- `背包玩法`\n- `1V1`\n- `策划案`\n- `核心玩法`\n- `系统功能`\n- `新手体验`\n- `商业化`\n- `活动`\n- `基建`\n- `音频`\n- `优化`\n- `赛事`\n\n## Branch Options (研发分支)\n\n- `master`\n- `【S11.5】`\n- `【S11.0】`\n- `【S10.6】`\n- `【1V1】删档测试 V0.95`\n- `【1V1】正式版本 V1.0`\n- `【S10.0】`\n- `YYZY_1V1_V1.0`\n- `YZY_1V1 V1.0 Beta`\n\n## User IDs\n\n| Name | TAPD User ID |\n|------|-------------|\n| 叶枝君 | `1415287364` |\n| 周以天(兵王) | `1166740146` |\n\n## Hidden Submit Buttons\n\n| ID | Name | Value | Action |\n|----|------|-------|--------|\n| `#save_view` | `data[submit]` | `提交&查看` | Create & view detail |\n| `#save_return` | `data[save_return]` | `提交&返回` | Create & return to list |\n| `#save_draft` | `data[save_draft]` | `保存草稿` | Save as draft |\n\n## Other Hidden Fields\n\n| Name | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `data[add_bug_token]` | CSRF token (auto-generated, value = userId + timestamp) |\n| `data[template_id]` | Bug template ID: `1131253609001000011` |\n| `data[return_url]` | Redirect after creation |\n| `data[type]` | Always `bugtemp` |\n| `data[is_new_status]` | Always `0` |\n| `data[is_editor_or_markdown]` | Editor type: `1` |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778849364428}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b896b82","parentId":"2f05253e","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:49:28.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need the TAPD user ID for 小骑士(谭佳钦). I don't have it in the reference files. Let me search my memory or check if I have it anywhere.\n\nFrom MEMORY.md:\n- 叶枝君 = `1415287364`\n- 周以天(兵王) = `1166740146`\n\nBut 谭佳钦(小骑士) is not listed. I'll need to either:\n1. Search for it somewhere\n2. Try to find it in TAPD\n3. Ask the master for it\n\nActually, let me check if I can find it in the TAPD page or if there's a way to look it up. The script has a handler field that takes a user ID. Let me check if maybe there's a way to search for the user.\n\nActually, the create_bug.mjs script uses `page.evaluate` to set the handler value directly as a user ID. So I need the TAPD user ID for 谭佳钦.\n\nLet me search memory for this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_1nQyByNjmTpTel0bLqma7651","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"谭佳钦 TAPD 用户ID user_id"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1155,"output":274,"cacheRead":69248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70677,"cost":{"input":0.0001617,"output":0.00007672000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001938944,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0021773639999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778849364429,"responseId":"59c8801f-e456-4a06-87c9-8d2c124b5dab"}}
