{"type":"message","id":"346d0e76","parentId":"f8079ea2","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:51:17.004Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ET_Ev5pIeppHuxbHRoj6YzY7885","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Handler field HTML:\n{\n  \"ownerHtml\": \"<input type=\\\"hidden\\\" id=\\\"BugCurrentOwner\\\" name=\\\"data[Bug][current_owner]\\\" userchooser=\\\"true\\\" required=\\\"required\\\" value=\\\"\\\">\",\n  \"ownerValHtml\": \"<input type=\\\"text\\\" data-control=\\\"pinyinuserchooser\\\" value=\\\"\\\" chooser-type=\\\"1\\\" required=\\\"required\\\" position=\\\"top\\\" title=\\\"处理人\\\" autohide=\\\"false\\\" id=\\\"BugCurrentOwnerValue\\\" data-src-path=\\\"https://www.tapd.cn/\\\" data-src-param=\\\"?workspace_id=31253609&amp;r=215\\\" autocomplete=\\\"off\\\" userchooser-init=\\\"true\\\">\",\n  \"s2idHtml\": \"NOT FOUND\",\n  \"allSelect2\": 0,\n  \"allSelect2Html\": \"\"\n}\n\nForm fields:\n{}\n\nScreenshot saved to tapd_form.png"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7261,"aggregated":"Handler field HTML:\n{\n  \"ownerHtml\": \"<input type=\\\"hidden\\\" id=\\\"BugCurrentOwner\\\" name=\\\"data[Bug][current_owner]\\\" userchooser=\\\"true\\\" required=\\\"required\\\" value=\\\"\\\">\",\n  \"ownerValHtml\": \"<input type=\\\"text\\\" data-control=\\\"pinyinuserchooser\\\" value=\\\"\\\" chooser-type=\\\"1\\\" required=\\\"required\\\" position=\\\"top\\\" title=\\\"处理人\\\" autohide=\\\"false\\\" id=\\\"BugCurrentOwnerValue\\\" data-src-path=\\\"https://www.tapd.cn/\\\" data-src-param=\\\"?workspace_id=31253609&amp;r=215\\\" autocomplete=\\\"off\\\" userchooser-init=\\\"true\\\">\",\n  \"s2idHtml\": \"NOT FOUND\",\n  \"allSelect2\": 0,\n  \"allSelect2Html\": \"\"\n}\n\nForm fields:\n{}\n\nScreenshot saved to tapd_form.png","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778849477004}}
{"type":"message","id":"b06e8154","parentId":"346d0e76","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:51:32.088Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the handler field structure:\n1. A HIDDEN field `#BugCurrentOwner` with the user ID\n2. A TEXT input `#BugCurrentOwnerValue` with `data-control=\"pinyinuserchooser\"` that shows the display name\n\nThis is a custom TAPD user chooser widget, NOT a Select2. It uses `pinyinuserchooser` which is TAPD's own autocomplete component. The approach needs to be different:\n\n1. Type into `#BugCurrentOwnerValue` to trigger the autocomplete dropdown\n2. Wait for the dropdown to appear\n3. Click on the matching user result\n4. The hidden `#BugCurrentOwner` should get populated automatically\n\nAlso, no form fields were found via the `for` attribute approach, which means the form structure might use a different labeling system.\n\nLet me try a different approach - use the user chooser properly by typing into the text input and waiting for the dropdown.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_sm02ySv1scEIHGl1CSm87494","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(__dirname, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\n\nconst STEALTH_INIT = () => {\n  delete navigator.webdriver;\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => false });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'languages', { get: () => ['zh-CN', 'zh'] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'hardwareConcurrency', { get: () => 8 });\n  window.chrome = { runtime: {}, loadTimes: function(){}, csi: function(){}, app: {} };\n};\n\nasync function main() {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  \n  const browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless: true,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']\n  });\n  \n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({\n    locale: 'zh-CN',\n    viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 },\n    userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/125.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n  });\n  \n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  await page.addInitScript(STEALTH_INIT);\n  \n  const url = `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/bugtrace/bugs/add`;\n  await page.goto(url, { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 }).catch(() => {});\n  await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n  \n  // Check if we're on the right page\n  const pageTitle = await page.title();\n  console.log('Page title:', pageTitle);\n  if (pageTitle.includes('WAF')) {\n    console.log('WAF blocked!');\n    await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(__dirname, 'tapd_waf.png') });\n    await browser.close();\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n  \n  // Fill title\n  await page.fill('#BugTitle', '卡组私密无法选中');\n  console.log('Title filled');\n  \n  // Select version\n  await page.selectOption('#BugVersionReport', '【1V1】正式版本V2.0');\n  console.log('Version selected');\n  \n  // Select module\n  await page.selectOption('#BugModule', '1V1');\n  console.log('Module selected');\n  \n  // Select priority\n  await page.selectOption('#BugPriority', 'P2');\n  console.log('Priority selected');\n  \n  // Set handler - Type \"谭佳钦\" into the user chooser\n  const handlerInput = page.locator('#BugCurrentOwnerValue');\n  await handlerInput.click();\n  await page.waitForTimeout(300);\n  await handlerInput.fill('谭佳钦');\n  await page.waitForTimeout(1500);\n  \n  // Check if dropdown appeared\n  const dropdownVisible = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    // Look for the popup container\n    const popup = document.querySelector('.ui-dialog,.pinyinuserchooser-popup,.userchooser-dropdown,[class*=chooser]');\n    if (popup) return 'POPUP: ' + popup.className.substring(0, 100);\n    \n    // Check if any new element appeared\n    const allDivs = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('div[style*=\"display\"][style*=\"block\"],div[style*=\"visible\"]'));\n    const chooserDivs = allDivs.filter(d => d.id?.includes('chooser') || d.className?.includes('chooser'));\n    if (chooserDivs.length) return 'CHOSER: ' + chooserDivs.length;\n    \n    // Look for list items\n    const uls = document.querySelectorAll('ul.ui-autocomplete,ul[class*=chooser],ul[class*=userchooser]');\n    if (uls.length) return 'UL_AUTO: ' + uls.length + ' ' + (uls[0].className || '');\n    \n    // Generic: check visible dropdown containers\n    const candidates = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.ui-menu,.ui-autocomplete,.autocomplete,ul[class*=suggest]'));\n    return 'CANDIDATES: ' + candidates.map(c => c.className).join(', ');\n  });\n  console.log('Dropdown status:', dropdownVisible);\n  \n  await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n  \n  // Try pressing Down + Enter to select\n  await page.keyboard.press('ArrowDown');\n  await page.waitForTimeout(300);\n  await page.keyboard.press('ArrowDown');\n  await page.waitForTimeout(300);\n  await page.keyboard.press('Enter');\n  await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n  \n  // Check if handler was set\n  const handlerValue = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const h = document.getElementById('BugCurrentOwner');\n    return { value: h?.value, display: document.getElementById('BugCurrentOwnerValue')?.value };\n  });\n  console.log('Handler after autocomplete:', JSON.stringify(handlerValue));\n  \n  // Screenshot before submit\n  await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(__dirname, 'tapd_before_submit.png') });\n  \n  // Submit\n  console.log('Submitting...');\n  await page.click('#save_return');\n  await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n  \n  const resultUrl = page.url();\n  console.log('Result URL:', resultUrl);\n  \n  if (!resultUrl.includes('bugs/add')) {\n    console.log('SUCCESS! Bug URL:', resultUrl);\n    await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(__dirname, 'tapd_success.png') });\n  } else {\n    console.log('Still on bug form - may have validation errors');\n    // Check for errors\n    const errors = await page.evaluate(() => {\n      const errEls = document.querySelectorAll('.error-message,.alert,.alert-error,[class*=error]');\n      const results = [];\n      errEls.forEach(el => {\n        if (el.textContent.trim()) results.push(el.textContent.trim().substring(0, 200));\n      });\n      return results.length ? results : document.body.innerText.substring(0, 1000);\n    });\n    console.log('Errors/Text:', errors);\n    await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(__dirname, 'tapd_error.png') });\n  }\n  \n  await browser.close();\n}\n\nmain().catch(e => {\n  console.error('Fatal:', e.message);\n  process.exit(1);\n});\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tapd_create_bug.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":233,"output":1816,"cacheRead":77952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80001,"cost":{"input":0.00003262,"output":0.0005084800000000001,"cacheRead":0.002182656,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002723756}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778849477006,"responseId":"f10d495c-8fed-43dc-a93d-665ab0bc1f92"}}
