{"type":"message","id":"252dfbc2","parentId":"26647006","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:54:11.526Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the handler clicked properly but the value is still `\"谭佳钦;\"` instead of a numeric user ID. After clicking on the suggestion:\n- `value`: `\"谭佳钦;\"` (name, not numeric ID)\n- `display`: `\"谭佳钦(谭佳钦);\"`\n\nThe hidden field got the NAME, not the ID. This means the TAPD Typeahead is returning the name instead of the numeric user ID.\n\nThe form still stayed on the same page after clicking submit. The issue might be:\n1. The handler value \"谭佳钦;\" is not a valid numeric user ID, so form validation fails\n2. The submit button might need a specific JavaScript event to work properly\n\nLooking at the form structure again, I notice the button `A#_view` has class `for_submit`. It probably uses JavaScript to click the corresponding hidden submit input. But maybe the form validation is stopping it because the handler value is invalid.\n\nLet me try a different approach - use `page.evaluate` to directly set the hidden field value to the correct user ID, then submit via JavaScript.\n\nBut I don't know 谭佳钦's TAPD ID! Let me try to:\n1. Check if I can find it in the page source (maybe there's a user list somewhere)\n2. Or try to use the autocomplete to search for 谭佳钦 and extract the ID from the data\n\nActually, maybe the autocomplete is returning data attributes with user IDs. Let me check the suggestion elements more carefully to find hidden data attributes.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_OGLTOPTpV1fSg1MsMwz70898","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(__dirname, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\n\nconst STEALTH_INIT = () => {\n  delete navigator.webdriver;\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => false });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'languages', { get: () => ['zh-CN', 'zh'] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'hardwareConcurrency', { get: () => 8 });\n  window.chrome = { runtime: {}, loadTimes: function(){}, csi: function(){}, app: {} };\n};\n\nasync function main() {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: true, args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'] });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({ locale: 'zh-CN', viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 }, userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36' });\n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  await page.addInitScript(STEALTH_INIT);\n  \n  const url = `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/bugtrace/bugs/add`;\n  await page.goto(url, { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 }).catch(() => {});\n  await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n  \n  const pageTitle = await page.title();\n  if (pageTitle.includes('WAF')) { console.log('WAF!'); await browser.close(); process.exit(1); }\n  \n  // Type 谭 to trigger autocomplete and inspect ALL data in the dropdown\n  await page.click('#BugCurrentOwnerValue');\n  await page.waitForTimeout(300);\n  await page.fill('#BugCurrentOwnerValue', '谭');\n  await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n  \n  // Try to find the suggestion container and its parent to get user data attributes\n  const dropdownInfo = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    // Find the TT dropdown container\n    const menu = document.querySelector('.tt-dropdown-menu, .typeahead-dropdown, [class*=tt]');\n    if (!menu) return { error: 'no menu found' };\n    \n    const result = { menuTag: menu.tagName, menuId: menu.id, menuClass: menu.className };\n    \n    // Check the parent of the menu\n    const parent = menu.parentElement;\n    if (parent) {\n      result.parentTag = parent.tagName;\n      result.parentId = parent.id;\n      result.parentClass = parent.className?.substring(0, 200);\n      // Check all children of parent\n      result.parentChildren = Array.from(parent.querySelectorAll('*')).slice(0, 20).map(el => ({\n        tag: el.tagName,\n        id: el.id,\n        cls: el.className?.substring(0, 100),\n        text: el.textContent?.trim().substring(0, 100),\n        html: el.outerHTML?.substring(0, 200),\n      }));\n    }\n    \n    return result;\n  });\n  \n  console.log('Dropdown info:');\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(dropdownInfo, null, 2));\n  \n  // Also check: is there a user data attribute in the body or script?\n  const userData = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    // Check for userchooser data in script tags\n    const scripts = document.querySelectorAll('script');\n    const userScripts = Array.from(scripts).filter(s => s.textContent?.includes('谭佳钦'));\n    return userScripts.map(s => s.textContent?.substring(0, 500));\n  });\n  console.log('\\nUser data in scripts:', JSON.stringify(userData, null, 2));\n  \n  await browser.close();\n}\n\nmain().catch(e => { console.error('Fatal:', e.message); process.exit(1); });\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tapd_inspect3.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":584,"output":1392,"cacheRead":90496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92472,"cost":{"input":0.00008176,"output":0.00038976,"cacheRead":0.0025338879999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0030054079999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778849638710,"responseId":"7e07c3d7-dfc8-4a28-97f8-3d0eee5c8a54"}}
