{"type":"message","id":"7bf92336","parentId":"ee8795d8","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:55:24.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All methods failed. The form stays on the same page regardless of how I try to submit. This likely means there's a form validation error. Looking at the page text, I notice the \"创建\" button is now visible but \"提交并继续创建\" and \"保存草稿\" are still there. No error messages are shown.\n\nThe most likely issue is that the handler field value \"谭佳钦;\" is invalid - it should be a numeric user ID. TAPD's form validation is blocking the submission because the handler field is either empty or has an invalid value.\n\nLet me check the console to see if there are any JavaScript errors, and also try to look at the form validation messages more carefully.\n\nActually, let me try a completely different approach. Instead of using the autocomplete, let me:\n1. Check the network tab for the user search API\n2. See what format the user ID data comes in\n3. Then set the hidden field directly with the correct numeric ID\n\nOr even simpler - let me try getting the user ID by looking at TAPD's user data. Let me check if the page has the user list embedded somewhere in a script tag or data attribute.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_oq7b017PZ2PSR2sXASiR5155","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(__dirname, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\n\nconst STEALTH_INIT = () => {\n  delete navigator.webdriver;\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => false });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'languages', { get: () => ['zh-CN', 'zh'] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'hardwareConcurrency', { get: () => 8 });\n  window.chrome = { runtime: {}, loadTimes: function(){}, csi: function(){}, app: {} };\n};\n\nasync function main() {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: true, args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'] });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({ locale: 'zh-CN', viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 }, userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36' });\n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  await page.addInitScript(STEALTH_INIT);\n  \n  // Listen for XHR requests to find the user search API\n  page.on('response', response => {\n    const reqUrl = response.url();\n    if (reqUrl.includes('user') || reqUrl.includes('User') || reqUrl.includes('member') || reqUrl.includes('chooser')) {\n      console.log('REQ:', reqUrl, response.status());\n    }\n  });\n  \n  const url = `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/bugtrace/bugs/add`;\n  await page.goto(url, { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 }).catch(() => {});\n  await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n  \n  // Type to trigger autocomplete and capture the XHR\n  await page.click('#BugCurrentOwnerValue');\n  await page.waitForTimeout(300);\n  await page.fill('#BugCurrentOwnerValue', '谭佳钦');\n  await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n  \n  // Check console messages\n  const consoleMsgs = [];\n  page.on('console', msg => {\n    if (msg.text().includes('user') || msg.text().includes('chooser') || msg.text().includes('error')) {\n      consoleMsgs.push(msg.text());\n    }\n  });\n  \n  // Try clicking suggestion\n  const sugg = page.locator('.tt-suggestion').first();\n  if (await sugg.isVisible()) {\n    await sugg.click();\n    await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n  }\n  \n  console.log('\\nConsole messages:', consoleMsgs.join('\\n'));\n  \n  // Check for hidden user ID data in DOM\n  const userIdData = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    // Check all data attributes on inputs\n    const inputs = document.querySelectorAll('input[data-userid],input[data-user-id],input[data-id]');\n    const results = [];\n    inputs.forEach(i => {\n      results.push({\n        id: i.id,\n        dataUserId: i.getAttribute('data-userid') || i.getAttribute('data-user-id') || i.getAttribute('data-id'),\n      });\n    });\n    \n    // Check for user data in localStorage/sessionStorage\n    const storage = {};\n    try {\n      for (let i = 0; i < localStorage.length; i++) {\n        const key = localStorage.key(i);\n        if (key.toLowerCase().includes('user') || key.toLowerCase().includes('member')) {\n          storage[key] = localStorage.getItem(key).substring(0, 200);\n        }\n      }\n    } catch(e) { storage.error = e.message; }\n    \n    // Check for user data embedded in script tags\n    const scripts = document.querySelectorAll('script[data-user]');\n    const scriptData = Array.from(scripts).map(s => ({\n      src: s.src,\n      data: s.getAttribute('data-user'),\n    }));\n    \n    return { inputs: results, storage, scriptData };\n  });\n  console.log('\\nUser ID data:', JSON.stringify(userIdData, null, 2));\n  \n  await browser.close();\n}\n\nmain().catch(e => { console.error('Fatal:', e.message); process.exit(1); });\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tapd_inspect4.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":565,"output":1372,"cacheRead":95232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97169,"cost":{"input":0.00007910000000000001,"output":0.00038416000000000004,"cacheRead":0.002666496,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003129756}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778849712026,"responseId":"a4dfaf7b-a44e-4c1a-8606-73bc791b94c2"}}
