{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f46d28690a0c2d8a5ff814efd4\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"om_x100b6f45ce0434a0b2405cca994ea0b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_fc5144301797fb813a1fee33e1130ac3\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"月圆之夜CCG开发群\",\n  \"sender\": \"小骑士(谭佳钦)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-05-15 22:12 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"月圆之夜CCG开发群\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true,\n  \"history_count\": 3\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"小骑士(谭佳钦) (ou_fc5144301797fb813a1fee33e1130ac3)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_fc5144301797fb813a1fee33e1130ac3\",\n  \"name\": \"小骑士(谭佳钦)\"\n}\n```\n\nReply target of current user message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"主人，bug 单已开好～\\n标题：卡组私密无法选中\\n处理人：谭佳钦\\\\(小骑士\\\\)\\n链接：[https://www.tapd.cn/tapd\\\\_fe/31253609/bug/detail/1131253609001016519](https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/bug/detail/1131253609001016519)\\n🌸\"\n}\n```\n\nChat history since last reply (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_e0cce20c6225d7dd0f16f55dc0d7440b\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1778850936862,\n    \"body\": \"藏羚羊(张璐颖): 啊啊啊啊周一去了我也要研究研究！！！\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_fc5144301797fb813a1fee33e1130ac3\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1778854119546,\n    \"body\": \"小骑士(谭佳钦): 虽然但是，我好像没收到单子[脸红]\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1778854249300,\n    \"body\": \"Yousan(叶枝君): ![image]\\n还在调教\"\n  }\n]\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"38ba9ed0","parentId":"06eec3d5","timestamp":"2026-05-15T14:12:25.440Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"9a047a94","parentId":"38ba9ed0","timestamp":"2026-05-15T14:12:44.181Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"小骑士在群里说\"单子能转给我吗\"，意思是虽然我开了单但处理人不是他，让我转给他。\n\n但是，回顾一下聊天记录：\n1. 主人说 \"开个bug单给@小骑士(谭佳钦), '卡组私密无法选中'\"\n2. 我创建了bug，处理人设置成了谭佳钦（用户ID 553342158）\n3. 小骑士回复说 \"虽然但是，我好像没收到单子[脸红]\"\n4. 主人回复 \"还在调教\"\n\n所以实际上bug单是设了谭佳钦为处理人的，但可能TAPD那边没有正确通知到他，或者处理人设置没生效？\n\n然后现在小骑士说\"单子能转给我吗\" - 他想让我把单子转给他。\n\n但是这是实际的TAPD操作，不是我能直接通过飞书完成的。我需要在TAPD里把bug单的处理人改成他。\n\n不过等等 - 这个bug单已经是设置他为处理人了啊。可能是TAPD的通知没发到，或者我要确认一下。\n\n让我看看小骑士的完整消息序列：\n1. \"虽然但是，我好像没收到单子[脸红]\" - 他说没收到单子\n2. Yousan回答 \"还在调教\" - 意思是还在调试自动化流程\n3. 小骑士又说 \"单子能转给我吗\"\n\n他可能是在问叶枝君（主人），而不是问我？\n\n但他是@我回复的（was_mentioned=true），所以是在问我。\n\n实际上，这单本来就是开给谭佳钦(小骑士)的，处理人设的就是他。可能是TAPD的通知他没收到的意思。\n\n等等，让我重新看看 - 小骑士说\"单子能转给我吗\"可能是真实的URL没被正确调转到他的账号去。可能是因为我刚才把处理人设置为他的用户ID `553342158`，但不确定是否正确。\n\n让我查一下这个bug现在TAPD里处理人是谁，或者我直接重新编辑一下这个bug，把处理人确认改为他。\n\n不过由于TAPD的API我不熟悉，我可以用Playwright登录TAPD，编辑这个bug，确认处理人是他。\n\n但等等，他的请求是\"单子能转给我吗\" - 这是个简单请求。如果单子已经是他了，我就告诉他单子已经是他的了。如果没设成功，我帮他再改一下。\n\n让我先检查一下这个bug单现在的状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"处理人本来就是设的你呀～让我确认一下。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_i2iWZOBfP0ehTAwj6wSe1057","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(__dirname, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\n\nconst STEALTH_INIT = () => {\n  delete navigator.webdriver;\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => false });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'languages', { get: () => ['zh-CN', 'zh'] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'hardwareConcurrency', { get: () => 8 });\n  window.chrome = { runtime: {}, loadTimes: function(){}, csi: function(){}, app: {} };\n};\n\nasync function main() {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: true, args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'] });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({ locale: 'zh-CN', viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 }, userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36' });\n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  await page.addInitScript(STEALTH_INIT);\n  \n  // Go to bug detail page\n  const bugUrl = `https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/bug/detail/1131253609001016519`;\n  await page.goto(bugUrl, { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 }).catch(() => {});\n  await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n  \n  const pageTitle = await page.title();\n  console.log('Page:', pageTitle);\n  \n  if (pageTitle.includes('WAF')) {\n    console.log('WAF blocked!');\n    await browser.close();\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n  \n  // Get bug info\n  const bugInfo = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    // Try to find owner/handler info\n    const bodyText = document.body.innerText;\n    \n    // Look for 处理人 or 负责人 text\n    const handlerLines = [];\n    const lines = bodyText.split('\\n');\n    let found = false;\n    for (let i = 0; i < lines.length; i++) {\n      if (lines[i].includes('处理人') || lines[i].includes('负责人') || lines[i].includes('当前处理')) {\n        handlerLines.push(lines[i].trim());\n        if (i + 1 < lines.length) handlerLines.push(lines[i + 1].trim());\n      }\n    }\n    \n    return {\n      title: document.title,\n      handlerInfo: handlerLines,\n      bodySnippet: bodyText.substring(0, 1000),\n    };\n  });\n  \n  console.log('Bug info:', JSON.stringify(bugInfo, null, 2));\n  \n  await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(__dirname, 'tapd_bug_detail.png') });\n  \n  await browser.close();\n}\n\nmain().catch(e => { console.error('Fatal:', e.message); process.exit(1); });\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tapd_check_bug.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":97439,"output":1394,"cacheRead":7424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106257,"cost":{"input":0.013641460000000001,"output":0.00039032000000000004,"cacheRead":0.000207872,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014239652}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778854345440,"responseId":"ab6a6697-65d8-44c4-b3d8-3fdafb8c7d7a"}}
