{"type":"message","id":"7d850ec7","parentId":"84330c27","timestamp":"2026-05-15T14:13:06.221Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ET_NK3GKQphn8LhxeqH8z1E1351","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Page: 卡组私密无法选中-月圆之夜-TAPD平台\nBug info: {\n  \"title\": \"卡组私密无法选中-月圆之夜-TAPD平台\",\n  \"handlerInfo\": [\n    \"处理人\",\n    \"评论\",\n    \"处理人\",\n    \"553342158\"\n  ],\n  \"bodySnippet\": \"主页\\n我的工作\\n我的文档\\n查询过滤\\n最近访问空间\\n月圆之夜\\n我参与的\\n公司管理\\n枝君\\n16\\n月月圆之夜\\n如何使用缺陷\\n项目仪表盘\\n需求\\n概览\\n缺陷\\n迭代\\n甘特图\\n更多\\n待处理\\nBUG\\n\\n卡组私密无法选中\\n\\nID: 1016519\\n详细信息\\n变更历史\\n(2)\\n需求\\n(0)\\n关联缺陷\\n(0)\\nGitlab关联\\n(0)\\n更多\\n暂无内容，点击编辑\\n编辑\\n标签\\n附件\\n评论\\n工作流\\n查看流程图\\n待处理 (当前)待验收取消暂时挂起\\n处理人\\n评论\\n插入\\n正文\\n苹果苹方\\n12px\\n流转\\n输入评论，@通知他人，ctrl + enter提交\\n基础信息\\n状态\\n待处理\\n创建模板\\n月圆之夜缺陷面板\\n发现版本\\n【1V1】正式版本V2.0\\n处理人\\n553342158\\n抄送人\\n叶枝君;\\n优先级\\nP2\\n研发分支\\nYYZY_1V1_V1.0\\n模块\\n1V1\\n创建人\\n叶枝君\\n创建时间\\n2026-05-15 20:56:32\\n修复人\\n-\\n解决方法\\n-\"\n}\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"calm-kelp","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"Page: 卡组私密无法选中-月圆之夜-TAPD平台\nBug info: {\n  \"title\": \"卡组私密无法选中-月圆之夜-TAPD平台\",\n  \"handlerInfo\": [\n    \"处理人\",\n    \"评论\",\n    \"处理人\",\n    \"553342158\"\n  ],\n  \"bodySnippet\": \"主页\\n我的工作\\n我的文档\\n查询过滤\\n最近访问空间\\n月圆之夜\\n我参与的\\n公司管理\\n枝君\\n16\\n月月圆之夜\\n如何使用缺陷\\n项目仪表盘\\n需求\\n概览\\n缺陷\\n迭代\\n甘特图\\n更多\\n待处理\\nBUG\\n\\n卡组私密无法选中\\n\\nID: 1016519\\n详细信息\\n变更历史\\n(2)\\n需求\\n(0)\\n关联缺陷\\n(0)\\nGitlab关联\\n(0)\\n更多\\n暂无内容，点击编辑\\n编辑\\n标签\\n附件\\n评论\\n工作流\\n查看流程图\\n待处理 (当前)待验收取消暂时挂起\\n处理人\\n评论\\n插入\\n正文\\n苹果苹方\\n12px\\n流转\\n输入评论，@通知他人，ctrl + enter提交\\n基础信息\\n状态\\n待处理\\n创建模板\\n月圆之夜缺陷面板\\n发现版本\\n【1V1】正式版本V2.0\\n处理人\\n553342158\\n抄送人\\n叶枝君;\\n优先级\\nP2\\n研发分支\\nYYZY_1V1_V1.0\\n模块\\n1V1\\n创建人\\n叶枝君\\n创建时间\\n2026-05-15 20:56:32\\n修复人\\n-\\n解决方法\\n-\"\n}\n","name":"cd C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace;"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778854386221}}
{"type":"message","id":"8a561555","parentId":"7d850ec7","timestamp":"2026-05-15T14:13:21.711Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the problem now! The bug was created, and I can see:\n\n**处理人: `553342158`** - This is the raw user ID, not the display name! TAPD is showing the numeric user ID instead of the name \"谭佳钦\". This means when I set the hidden field value to `553342158`, TAPD accepted it but the UI is showing the raw ID instead of the resolved name.\n\nSo the autocomplete didn't properly set the user - I manually set the hidden field value, but the display name didn't get properly associated. The bug is assigned to user 553342158 in the database, but it's showing as raw ID.\n\nThe fix would be to use the autocomplete properly - type the name and select from the dropdown, which should set both the hidden value AND the display text properly.\n\nLet me edit the bug to set the handler correctly using the autocomplete. I need to go to the edit page (or use the detail page's edit feature) and properly select 谭佳钦 from the autocomplete dropdown.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"处理人是设成你了，但显示的是原始ID `553342158` 而不是名字。说明自动补全没走对。我帮你重新编辑一下，让名字正确显示。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ttiW5N3hsNOUWsbOEP9B3450","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(__dirname, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\nconst BUG_ID = '1131253609001016519';\n\nconst STEALTH_INIT = () => {\n  delete navigator.webdriver;\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => false });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'languages', { get: () => ['zh-CN', 'zh'] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'hardwareConcurrency', { get: () => 8 });\n  window.chrome = { runtime: {}, loadTimes: function(){}, csi: function(){}, app: {} };\n};\n\nasync function main() {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: true, args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'] });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({ locale: 'zh-CN', viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 }, userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36' });\n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  await page.addInitScript(STEALTH_INIT);\n  \n  // Go to bug edit page \n  const editUrl = `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id=${BUG_ID}`;\n  await page.goto(editUrl, { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 }).catch(() => {});\n  await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n  \n  const pageTitle = await page.title();\n  console.log('Page:', pageTitle);\n  if (pageTitle.includes('WAF') || pageTitle.includes('waf')) { \n    // Try the other URL format\n    console.log('Trying alternative URL...');\n    await page.goto(`https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/${WORKSPACE_ID}/bug/detail/${BUG_ID}`, { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 }).catch(() => {});\n    await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n    \n    // Look for edit button\n    const editBtn = page.locator('text=编辑').first();\n    if (await editBtn.isVisible()) {\n      console.log('Clicking edit...');\n      await editBtn.click();\n      await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n    }\n  }\n  \n  // Find the handler input and fix it\n  const hasEditor = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    return {\n      hasOwnerInput: !!document.getElementById('BugCurrentOwner'),\n      hasOwnerValue: !!document.getElementById('BugCurrentOwnerValue'),\n      url: location.href,\n    };\n  });\n  console.log('Editor state:', JSON.stringify(hasEditor));\n  \n  if (hasEditor.hasOwnerInput) {\n    // Use the autocomplete properly\n    await page.click('#BugCurrentOwnerValue');\n    await page.waitForTimeout(300);\n    \n    // Clear first\n    await page.fill('#BugCurrentOwnerValue', '');\n    await page.waitForTimeout(300);\n    \n    // Type name character by character\n    await page.fill('#BugCurrentOwnerValue', '谭佳钦');\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n    \n    // Click the suggestion\n    const sugg = page.locator('.tt-suggestion').first();\n    if (await sugg.isVisible()) {\n      await sugg.click();\n      await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n      \n      // Check the result\n      const hv = await page.evaluate(() => ({\n        value: document.getElementById('BugCurrentOwner')?.value,\n        display: document.getElementById('BugCurrentOwnerValue')?.value,\n      }));\n      console.log('After autocomplete:', JSON.stringify(hv));\n      \n      // If value is still the name and not ID, we need to fix\n      if (hv.display && !hv.display.includes('553342158')) {\n        // Clear and try again with slower input\n        await page.fill('#BugCurrentOwnerValue', '');\n        await page.waitForTimeout(300);\n        await page.type('#BugCurrentOwnerValue', '谭佳钦', { delay: 200 });\n        await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n        \n        const sugg2 = page.locator('.tt-suggestion').first();\n        if (await sugg2.isVisible()) {\n          await sugg2.click();\n          await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n        }\n        \n        const hv2 = await page.evaluate(() => ({\n          value: document.getElementById('BugCurrentOwner')?.value,\n          display: document.getElementById('BugCurrentOwnerValue')?.value,\n        }));\n        console.log('After retry:', JSON.stringify(hv2));\n      }\n    }\n    \n    // Submit\n    console.log('Saving...');\n    const saveBtn = page.locator('#save_view, #_view, text=保存').first();\n    if (await saveBtn.isVisible()) {\n      await saveBtn.click();\n      await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n      console.log('Saved, URL:', page.url());\n    }\n  } else {\n    console.log('No editor form found, on detail page');\n    // Try clicking edit on the detail page\n    const editLinks = await page.evaluate(() => {\n      const links = [];\n      document.querySelectorAll('a, button, span, div').forEach(el => {\n        if (el.textContent?.trim() === '编辑' || el.textContent?.trim().includes('编辑')) {\n          links.push({\n            tag: el.tagName,\n            id: el.id,\n            cls: el.className?.substring(0, 80),\n            text: el.textContent?.trim(),\n            visible: el.offsetParent !== null,\n          });\n        }\n      });\n      return links;\n    });\n    console.log('Edit links:', JSON.stringify(editLinks));\n  }\n  \n  await page.screenshot({ path: path.join(__dirname, 'tapd_edit.png') });\n  await browser.close();\n}\n\nmain().catch(e => { console.error('Fatal:', e.message); process.exit(1); });\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tapd_fix_handler.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":392,"output":1769,"cacheRead":106496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108657,"cost":{"input":0.00005488,"output":0.00049532,"cacheRead":0.002981888,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003532088}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778854386223,"responseId":"5a837c88-beb3-4947-8d1f-6ac7c3c80933"}}
